  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators' hypothesis is that measuring the PCTdynamics would be an easy and
      reliable symptom to evaluate in pathologies affecting the optic nerve
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Physiopathologic study aiming to assess the interest of measuring the lenght of pupil cycle
      in the dynamic study of the pupillary light reflex.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
